thread.title: Coronation Street

author: Fiona Flynn
title: Coronation Street
text: Kylie is desperate to stop Sarah from talking to the police tonight as she finds a very jittery Sarah at the station ready to confess all. Will she be able to keep her quiet? For now maybe, but that girl is going to crack, and soon. Elsewhere, Carla, Aidan, Johnny and Kate discuss the factory over dinner in the Bistro. Johnny confirms that he's on board with the factory on two conditions - that he's central to the running of the business and that they find a job for Kate. Not sure how well Carla will handle all this bossiness though...
